src_text: Tona ya Dit helete, Enoch Godongwana, o tla aba MTBPS ka Palamenteng ka Labone la 11 Dibatsela 2021.
trg_text: Ms Makano Mosid 8.

src_text: Setatamente se se tla ala ka botlalo ditoki o go matlotlo a boset haba go netefat a gore matlotlo a set haba e ba ao a swarelelag
trg_text: from 25 November (International Day of No Violence against Women) to 10 December (International Human Rights Day)
